        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—Or, “And after the death of Hezron in Caleb-ephratah—and the wife of Hezron was Abiah—and she bare him Ashur . . .” The text is evidently corrupt. The best suggestion is based on the reading of the LXX.: ",
        "children": []
